Phyllis Gordon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phyllis_Gordon 0 Phyllis Gordon (October 17, 1889 – October 16, 1964) was an American actress. She appeared in 50 silent era and sound era motion pictures between 1911 and 1941. She was born in Suffolk, Virginia, and died at age 74 in Sonoma, California.Gordon was once notably photographed walking a pet cheetah on a London shopping street. She also "shocked" people at a restaurant in Davenport, Iowa, when they realized that she had a marmoset in her handbag.
